&gt; Hi Divyansh,
&gt;
&gt; Thanks for the links, I think that the &quot;meaning&quot; in &quot;allowed values and
&gt; meaning&quot; is supposed to imply that the same processing model and algorithm
&gt; should be used. I do think it would be better if the SVG spec was more
&gt; explicit, but that's practically an editorial concern.
&gt;
&gt; If there is any difference at all between SVG &lt;a&gt; and HTML &lt;a&gt; in how
&gt; these four attributes are handled I think that needs to be spec'd and
&gt; tested, but if it's all the same then this seems straightforward.
&gt;
&gt; LGTM1
