&gt; *Cc:* blink-dev &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="60020c090e0b4d040516200308120f0d09150d4e0f1207"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
&gt; *Subject:* [EXTERNAL] Re: [blink-dev] Intent to Ship: Support ping,
