&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; ECMA402 is merged in &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/tc39/ecma402/pull/960"&gt;https://github.com/tc39/ecma402/pull/960&lt;/a&gt; and
