&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class="darkgray font13"&gt;
&lt;span class="sender pipe"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=from:%22%27Johann+Hofmann%27+via+blink%5C-dev%22" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;'Johann Hofmann' via blink-dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20251109" rel="nofollow"&gt;Sun, 09 Nov 2025 17:31:30 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
