On Wed, Nov 5, 2025 at 6:47 PM Daniel Bratell &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="3a58485b4e5f561414147a5d575b535614595557"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:

