&gt;&gt; went to plenary.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/tc39/ecma402/blob/main/meetings/notes-2025-05-08.md#normative-add-localeprototypegetvariants-960"&gt;https://github.com/tc39/ecma402/blob/main/meetings/notes-2025-05-08.md#normative-add-localeprototypegetvariants-960&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; On Wed, Nov 5, 2025 at 2:03 PM Frank Tang (譚永鋒) &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="3452401a1a1a74535b5b5358511a575b59"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
