&gt;&gt;&gt; On Wed, Nov 5, 2025 at 6:00 AM Chris Harrelson &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7112190318025f5f5f311219031e1c18041c5f1e0316"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
