&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; On Wed, Oct 22, 2025 at 7:08 AM 'Philip Jägenstedt' via blink-dev &lt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="ee8c828780c0c0c0ae8d869c8183879b83c0819c89"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
