&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; link to the spec, and a standards position for Mozilla was filed:
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color/#predefined-display-p3-linear"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color/#predefined-display-p3-linear&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/mozilla/standards-positions/issues/1311"&gt;https://github.com/mozilla/standards-positions/issues/1311&lt;/a&gt;
