On Thu, Oct 23, 2025 at 10:07 AM Dale Curtis &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="d5b1b4b9b0b6a0a7fbfbfb95b6bda7bab8bca0b8fbbaa7b2"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
