&lt;pre&gt;

Hi Alex,&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

Google Meet needs this functionality. It gives WebRTC-based apps better 
control over video quality and performance. It has been reviewed and 
approved &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://www.w3.org/2025/09/16-webrtc-minutes.html#cb3e"&gt;https://www.w3.org/2025/09/16-webrtc-minutes.html#cb3e&lt;/a&gt;&gt; by 
representatives of Mozilla, Meta, Apple and Microsoft at a WebRTC WG 
meeting. This is a small, incremental change that exposes an existing mode 
&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://webrtc-review.googlesource.com/c/src/+/415200"&gt;https://webrtc-review.googlesource.com/c/src/+/415200&lt;/a&gt;&gt; to JS.

Regards,
Sergey

