&lt;pre&gt;Ok, sounds good. Requesting lgtms for the warning phase then. Will we need
a separate chromestatus later to request approval for the enforcement phase?&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

On Wed, Oct 22, 2025 at 4:03 PM Vladimir Levin &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="5e28332e7070701e3d362c3133372b3370312c39"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:

