&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; IdPs failing to update .well-known/web-identity for FedCM client
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; metadata risk breaking authentication flows. Chrome 143 issues warnings,
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; but starting Chrome 145, missing accounts_endpoint or login_url will block
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; configurations entirely. Immediate migration is critical to maintain
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; compatibility and avoid service disruptions for relying parties and
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; end-users.
