&lt;pre&gt;These are just event handler attributes, but for larger Gamepad API changes
it would indeed to be nice to consider device mocking for testing. I think
something like this for Bluetooth might be a pattern to follow:
&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/web-platform-tests/wpt/blob/master/infrastructure/testdriver/bidi/bluetooth/simulate_adapter.https.html"&gt;https://github.com/web-platform-tests/wpt/blob/master/infrastructure/testdriver/bidi/bluetooth/simulate_adapter.https.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

