&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Web Feature ID*
&gt;&gt; Missing feature
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; *Motivation*
&gt;&gt; The existing &lt;input type=text list=datalist&gt; HTML form element is not
&gt;&gt; sufficient for web developers due to lack of supported content and
&gt;&gt; customization. As a result, web developers must build their own which
&gt;&gt; creates usability and accessibility risks.
